title: Episode 203: Juice Kits and Creamed Corn (Feat. Trouble)
itunes:title: Episode 203: Juice Kits and Creamed Corn (Feat. Trouble)
description:
Atlanta rapper, Trouble, is back by popular demand for this week's episode of Lip Service. Trouble explains how the cucumber challenge took off on social media, opens up about issues with his newest baby mother, and much more. Enjoy!
